  <brief_title>Hyaluronic Acid Gel in Prevention of Intrauterine Adhesions After Endometrial Ablation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Autocrosslinked Hyaluronic Acid Gel in Prevention of Intrauterine Adhesions After Bipolar Radiofrequency Endometrial Ablation: a Randomised, Controlled and Double Blind Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
